Microsoft Outlook
-----------------

* Preferences -> General -> Uncheck "Group similar folders"
* Preferences -> Notifications and Sounds -> Uncheck Sounds
* Preferences -> Reading -> Mark mail as read: after 1 seconds
* Preferences -> Reading -> Uncheck "Highlight messages from the same conversation"
* Preferences -> Composing -> Uncheck "Compose messages in HTML"
* Preferences -> Calendar -> Default reminder: 5 minutes

* View -> Arrange By -> Account
* View -> Reading Pane -> Below
* View -> Hide Toolbar
* View -> Columns: Attachment, From, Subject, Date Received
